column5: For all the members celebrating Chinese New Year!  Kung Hei Fat Choy!  May all of you have Good Health, Prosperity, Good Fortune, and Good FISHING in the New Year!  Stan Wu (HearingFish)
Hey! another chinese on OFC(didn't notice much before  )! well i wish everyone the best for the new year and best of health.
May the Year of the Golden Pig bring prosperity to your family! Kung Hey Fatt Choy from the Guay Lo.
I see GOOGLE has made note of this event as well. Cheers!
